18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都殺唔到佢, 一殺就閃，再電你</blockquote><br />\n但係佢殺到我冇哂耐性嬲嬲豬走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢最後睇我4桃牌我就已經笑到抽筋"},{"pid":"ec420e3c7ec57017b890ccbf444f4056e73a62a8","tid":266062,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:21:32.000Z","msg":"識留樂你收左皮好耐"},{"pid":"bfd3fde3397004c2c9d4b83c17043d5ef89fd084","tid":266062,"uid":82816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"送3牌先回1血 你邊夠牌用<br />\n對面玩得屎姐"},{"pid":"b840f81a84351d56dddf712299439a87ccff85dd","tid":266062,"uid":44780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"樓主 係十夫長？"},{"pid":"4a05626b6624b778f969afb9ab1f5bcf19e30f5c","tid":266062,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:32:32.000Z","msg":"其實仲可以慢慢打呀 唔明點解佢要走"},{"pid":"1b9b526f94683828fabbbd9d66b51e147f87f4bb","tid":266062,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識留樂你收左皮好耐</blockquote><br />\n滿血中樂又點？"},{"pid":"6b03b4c897de2448ad643a4a9f61fa0132e40301","tid":266062,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識留樂你收左皮好耐</blockquote><br />\n滿血中樂又點？</blockquote><br />\n殺1血<br />\n樂不<br />\n棄一張<br />\n下回送多兩張殺比佢回返滿血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28e9dc5d5cc7006779c6e3ffeea6050795f66f4","tid":266062,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"樓主淨打表情唔講嘢都幾摟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158c51b863ae77bb3f3fce8849bd93d8c3e5aa6a","tid":266062,"uid":57303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送3牌先回1血 你邊夠牌用<br />\n對面玩得屎姐</blockquote><br />\n冇血+冇牌咪用再起囉<br />\n有牌咪送殺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/